# Faberon modals

- Register each modal in `store/modals/types.ts` with typed `data` and callbacks.
- Implement the modal container under `src/modals` and switch on it in `ModalsHost`.
- Open with `useModalsStore().open(name, options)`; close pops the LIFO stack top.
- Do not mount named modals from pages or keep open state in page-local `useState`.
- Modal containers receive stack entry options as props; `ModalsHost` decides what to display.
- Use `components/Modal` for shared shell and backdrop.
